<th scope="row" class="navbox-group" style=";width:7.4em;padding-left:0em;padding-right:0em;font-weight:normal;background:#dd9;;">
<div style="padding:0em 0.75em;"><a href="Chronometry" title="Chronometry">Chronometry</a></div>
</th>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
